# NCF Runtime Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Human[Human Approver]
    Orchestrator[Content Orchestrator]
    Queue[Task Queue]
    EventBus[Event Bus]
    Agents[Agent Workers]
    Memory[Memory Retrieval Service]
    Validation[Validation Service]
    Approval[Approval Service]
    ToolRouter[Tool Router]
    Registries[Registries]
    Platforms[External Platforms]
    Metrics[Metrics & Observability]

    Human --> Approval
    Orchestrator --> Queue
    Queue --> Agents
    Agents --> EventBus

    Agents --> Memory
    Agents --> Validation
    Agents --> Approval
    Agents --> ToolRouter

    ToolRouter --> Platforms

    Agents --> Registries
    EventBus --> Registries

    Registries --> Metrics
    Platforms --> Metrics
```
